@startuml
object Teacher
object "Attendance API" as AttendanceAPI
object "Attendance update" as AttendanceUpdate
object "Attendance storage" as AttendanceStorage
object "Session finance sync" as SessionFinanceSync
object "Finance storage" as FinanceStorage
object Database <<database>>
Teacher --> AttendanceAPI : 1: attendance command
AttendanceAPI --> AttendanceUpdate : 2: execute
AttendanceUpdate --> AttendanceStorage : 3: load session/class/student
AttendanceStorage --> Database : 4: SELECT validation rows
AttendanceUpdate --> AttendanceStorage : 5: load enrollment at session time
AttendanceUpdate --> AttendanceStorage : 6: save manual attendance
AttendanceStorage --> Database : 7: INSERT/UPDATE attendance
AttendanceUpdate --> SessionFinanceSync : 8: sync fee projection
SessionFinanceSync --> FinanceStorage : 9: write Fee record
FinanceStorage --> Database : 10: UPSERT/DELETE Fee record
AttendanceUpdate --> AttendanceAPI : 11: Attendance
@enduml
